{"tid":2083968,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"反警暴有甚麼錯？ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-06-29T05:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T06:01:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2c71af64aca18cbb5ff585f563a4f48796ce19a2","tid":2083968,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:51:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200629/20945848/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200629%2F20945848%2F&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8f7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=91887f1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200629%2F20945848%2F&h=d1d7ba0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200629/20945848/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n反警暴有甚麼錯？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200629/large/1593338965_1813.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200629%2Flarge%2F1593338965_1813.jpg&h=807e248f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方與紅十字會舉辦捐血活動，引發不愉快事件，最後警方腰斬是次活動，而紅十字會更要公開道歉。據悉原因是其中一名紅十字會工作人員胸口佩戴了一個反警暴的飾物，令群警不滿。<br />\n<br />\n這就奇怪了，香港人甚麼時候連佩戴飾物的權利都消失了？而香港警察幾時擁有凌駕法律的特權，以他們的個人喜好去管束香港人佩戴甚麼樣的飾物？<br />\n<br />\n更奇怪的是，反警暴有甚麼錯？不管是不是警暴受害人，不管你是<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n反警暴呀！難道香港警察不反警暴，而支持警暴？<br />\n<br />\n甚麼叫「警暴」，就是警察濫權、行使暴力。「警暴」是正常警<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n席，而不是反對「反警暴」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，後來有消息指出，該名工作人員當日佩戴的只是一<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n裝備嗎？更何況那不是一個頭盔，只是一個頭盔掛飾。<br />\n<br />\n香港警察的行為已經不是一般的濫權，而是非理性、反邏<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n中心嚴肅跟進。跟進甚麼？香港人佩戴黃色頭盔飾物都有罪嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"26996b454d0c37600308cf39654176af9f2527a1","tid":2083968,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:53:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56676df0b3704f2bff3e8148dfc80b03739ae887","tid":2083968,"uid":76794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:01:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}